{"tid":1740771,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全民豬嘴！！","createTime":"2019-11-20T05:09:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T05:18:42.000Z","uid":307371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4893b665d018368d68916fa731bbd6fe0f226093","tid":1740771,"uid":307371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:09:02.000Z","msg":"有無諗過，既然蒙面法又無咗，然後條條街都二噁英含量超標<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一於<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民豬嘴</span></span></strong>！直程連學生都要戴豬嘴返學保護自己。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好處如下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">一、畫面震撼</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以打國際牌，再加強香港進入作戰狀況既形象。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">二、保護手足</span></ins></span></strong><br />\n無論勇武和理非，依家出到黎tg係最低消費。如果逃走既時候畀狗搜到豬嘴會照拉。但如果全民豬嘴就可以減低大家被捕風險，裝都唔洗棄。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實行困難：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">一、物資短缺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n現時豬嘴短缺，要買都未必買到。但如果全民買，需求增加，供應按道理都會增加。加上少咗棄裝果條數，長遠黎講都可行。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">二、價格高昂</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n靚少少都三四百一個嘴，有學生可能負擔唔起。但依家大條道理為健康着想，就黎你唔返學留係屋企都有機會中tg，問屋企攞個，係telegram r文具，有好多方法可幫助大家。就算學生真係負擔唔起，由大人，打工仔開始全民豬嘴都係叫做好既開始。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">P牌仔第一次出pn 請多多見諒</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d617b150a26d5aba89d0f1c51ca4d6f943dc6c8","tid":1740771,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:09:27.000Z","msg":"如果你覺得勇武暫時要休息，咁作為和理非嘅你請今晚出場，今晚有行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1740320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1740320</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好剩係推，記住Facebook，IG，Twitter，WhatsApp ，TG 都廣傳！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VvOpzbk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVvOpzbk.jpg&h=32cced46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bBOg9KG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbBOg9KG.jpg&h=35bd8f5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64ab2ca428e39671f41f1a7e246afc2ceb49e0b0","tid":1740771,"uid":307371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:10:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"82ac7cd9e9b54982da072e705fdfeea8947b067c","tid":1740771,"uid":65353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:10:54.000Z","msg":"戴住聽日出黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4PHmBHV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4PHmBHV.png&h=52b0d6ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8cd4310ae3bbe2df78898ac15350d7aef8e6d590","tid":1740771,"uid":307371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:11:09.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"0b24b1b32739ddf3ae2750b9a5c43d8644b46e6b","tid":1740771,"uid":307371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:11:23.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"7529a21a3a842b2c47a04356874ad50221ccacb5","tid":1740771,"uid":307371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:11:35.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"7f4687fab2f0631609735248ca833c3dbc3dddb2","tid":1740771,"uid":307371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:11:45.000Z","msg":"推4/10"},{"pid":"43e